snippet.title: Best VGM 2420 - Bomberman World - Area 1 ~ Planet Forest
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PS1
Bomberman World (1998)
Area 1 ~ Planet Forest
Hironao Yamamoto & Jun Chikuma
